<%= @store_name %> — Acompanhamento de Pedido
==========================================

<% if @is_paid %>
PEDIDO CONFIRMADO!
Recebemos seu pagamento com sucesso.<% if @order.customer_email.present? %>
Enviamos a confirmação para <%= @order.customer_email %>.<% end %>
<% else %>
<%= @subject_base %>
<% end %>

Pedido: <%= @order.number %>
Data:   <%= @order.created_at.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %>
Status: <%= OrderStatusHistory.title_for(@status) %>
<% if @is_paid && @payment_ref %>
Ref:    <%= @payment_ref %>
<% end %>

Acompanhe seu pedido em:
<%= @public_url %>

---
<% unless @is_paid %>

HISTÓRICO
---------
<% @history.reverse.each do |entry| %>
✓ <%= entry.title %> — <%= entry.created_at.strftime("%d/%m/%Y %H:%M") %>
<% end %>

---
<% end %>
<% if @show_promise %>

PRAZO DE ENVIO
--------------
Seu pedido será preparado e enviado até <%= @order.promised_completion_date.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %>.
Algumas peças são artesanais e feitas sob demanda. O prazo da transportadora será contado a partir do envio.

---
<% end %>

RESUMO DO PEDIDO
----------------
<% @items_view.each do |item| %>
• <%= item[:name] %><% if item[:size].present? %> (Tam. <%= item[:size] %>)<% end %> [<%= item[:fulfillment_mode] == "made_to_order" ? "Sob encomenda" : "Pronta entrega" %>]
  <%= item[:quantity] %> un. × R$ <%= format("%.2f", item[:unit_price_cents] / 100.0) %> = R$ <%= format("%.2f", item[:subtotal_cents] / 100.0) %>
<% end %>

Subtotal: R$ <%= format("%.2f", @order.items_total_cents / 100.0) %>
<% if @order.shipping_fee_cents.to_i > 0 %>
Frete:    R$ <%= format("%.2f", @order.shipping_fee_cents / 100.0) %>
<% end %>
Total:    R$ <%= format("%.2f", @order.total_cents / 100.0) %>
Pagamento: <%= @order.payment_summary %>

<% if @is_paid %>
---

CONTATO
-------
<% if @order.customer_name.present?  %><%= @order.customer_name  %>
<% end %><% if @order.customer_email.present? %><%= @order.customer_email %>
<% end %><% if @order.customer_phone.present? %><%= @order.customer_phone %>
<% end %>

ENTREGA
-------
<% if @is_pickup %>
Retirada presencial
<% elsif @shipping_fields[:address].present? %>
<%
  address_line = "#{@shipping_fields[:address]}"
  address_line += ", #{@shipping_fields[:number]}" if @shipping_fields[:number].present?
  city_state   = @shipping_fields[:city].present? \
    ? "#{@shipping_fields[:city]}#{" - #{@shipping_fields[:state]}" if @shipping_fields[:state].present?}" \
    : nil
  address_parts = [
    address_line,
    @shipping_fields[:complement].presence,
    city_state,
    @shipping_fields[:cep].present? ? "CEP #{@shipping_fields[:cep]}" : nil
  ].compact
%>
<%= address_parts.join(" · ") %>
<% if @order.carrier.present? %><%= @order.carrier %><%= " · #{@order.shipping_service}" if @order.shipping_service.present? %>
<% end %><% end %>

---

Use o link de acompanhamento acima para visualizar o status, o rastreio
e — se for o caso — cancelar itens artesanais ainda não enviados.

<% end %>
<% if @order.tracking_code.present? %>
---

RASTREIO
--------
Código: <%= @order.tracking_code %>
<% if @order.carrier.present? %>
Transportadora: <%= @order.carrier %><%= " (#{@order.shipping_service})" if @order.shipping_service.present? %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

